Class NodeIterableImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.gephi.graph.dhns.graph.iterators.NodeIterableImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Node>, NodeIterable
public class NodeIterableImpl
extends Object
implements NodeIterable

Implementation of NodeIterable with automatic lock unlocking when hasNext returns false.

The doBreak method has to be called if the loop is interrupted.

Author:
Mathieu Bastian
